			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;should&quot;_with_&quot;yinggai&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;should&quot; with &quot;yinggai&quot;">Expressing "should" with "yinggai"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK3</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;had_better&quot;_with_&quot;haishi&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;had better&quot; with &quot;haishi&quot;">Expressing "had better" with "haishi"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK4</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;must&quot;_with_&quot;dei&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;must&quot; with &quot;dei&quot;">Expressing "must" with "dei"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK4</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-usedfor clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Used for</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="Expressing_attitude" title="Expressing attitude">Expressing attitude</a> </div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-keywords clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Keywords</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="好" title="好">好</a>, <a href="最" title="最">最</a>, <a href="最好" title="最好">最好</a></div>
		</li>
		
	</ul>
	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki-hao.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki-hao.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Chinese-grammar-wiki-hao.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-hao.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Chinese-grammar-wiki-hao.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-hao.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Chinese-grammar-wiki-hao.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-hao.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div> 
<p>Sure, 最好 (zuìhǎo) means "best." But it can also be used to mean "it would be best to" or "had better." It is often used when giving advice to someone or even politely making demands.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="Expressing_&quot;had_better&quot;_with_&quot;zuihao&quot;#Positive_Form"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Positive Form</span></a>
<ul>
